    Type

    public static class Type.CapturedUndetVar
extends Type.UndetVar
    This class is used to represent synthetic captured inference variables that can be generated during nested generic method calls. The only difference between these inference variables and ordinary ones is that captured inference variables cannot get new bounds through incorporation.
